<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=5265&amp;p=47494#p47494"><![CDATA[
The "V=T" update happens at cycle 304 of the pre-render scanline, so anything before that is ok.  Any full updates of both T and V can even be done between 304 and 341 with no artifacts for the first visible scanline.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Sun May 31, 2009 6:45 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
